core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:20:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=18474847&amp;category_guid=vice&amp;sup_id=16510417&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20131023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D18474847%26category_guid%3Dvice%26sup_id%3D16510417%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20131023&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=77007316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D18474847%26category_guid%3Dvice%26sup_id%3D16510417%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20131023&h=0afa5a27\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=18474847&amp;category_guid=vice&amp;sup_id=16510417&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20131023</a>"},{"pid":"9c0a823e61ca6e86dddb79e2c5e72c9a1c3f05cc","tid":260691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-EPNGJsdb88o/UpyQ_dUdrAI/AAAAAAAAI1o/ypc032uo_4w/w600-h595-no/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh5.googleusercontent.com%2F-EPNGJsdb88o%2FUpyQ_dUdrAI%2FAAAAAAAAI1o%2Fypc032uo_4w%2Fw600-h595-no%2F1.jpg&h=570f7db8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3373b91624d38ad3573a2aec962766c4f384ff90","tid":260691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:30:53.000Z","msg":"網民熱話：3張總成本估計約85,000元新歇腳櫈得單座位　街坊點傾偈？<br />\n<br />\n07月11日(二) 18:02<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170711/photo/bkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170711183927\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170711%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170711183927&h=614d4687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社區設施好壞影響市民的生活質素，有網民今日在Facebook群組「西環變幻時」中上載圖片，指出西環山市街的斜路新建椅子工程已經竣工，新建有3張總成本估計約85,000元的單座位歇腳櫈讓街坊休憩。然而有街坊發現，有別舊櫈有雙座位設計，每張獨立裝設的歇腳櫈相隔甚遠又沒有上蓋，加上椅子下建有基座，擔心會絆倒老人家，令人質疑櫈子的實用性及價值。<br />\n<br />\n「山市街新座椅裝好咗喇！ 」網民Fio Fion Fiona&lrm;今日在Facebook群組上載3張社區內新建歇腳櫈的相片，分享工程已竣工。該批櫈子屬山市街座椅重置工程，經2016年中西區地區小型工程計劃撥款興建，當時總工程預算約為85,000元，即每張座椅成本約為28,000元。<br />\n<br />\n網民看見此新椅後都議論紛紛。先是選址方面，有人認為不應建在沒遮蔭的地方：「日曬雨淋邊個會坐」；有人則覺得單座位不利街坊聊天，而最令人憂慮的是椅子下的台階，網民擔心台階會絆倒老人家。其次價錢亦是討論的重點，有網民認為工程貴得不合理，但有人亦試圖為工程成本解畫：「地底可能有管道線管等，要升高一些。公平一些天氣有熱有涼，不能滿足每一個人眼球需要。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170711/bkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170711%2Fbkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001.html&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=af756ef6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170711/bkn-20170711180208904-0711_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"347b2077682a028e1d2f17473462eedf35d81f7f","tid":260691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:38:46.000Z","msg":"超出每小時發表主題數量上限，請稍候再試"},{"pid":"4f8ce4a273f6043145450453a60076024d004bf2","tid":260691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://myhome-idea.com/goods-392.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyhome-idea.com%2Fgoods-392.html&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=14b41326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://myhome-idea.com/goods-392.html</a>"},{"pid":"fad3b46346caf3176f94f3c92dba17e37ea8dcfe","tid":260691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:47:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?ut_sk=1.t7exUfP%2BUtMQADw88j9OJaVf_21380790_1407271417.Copy.ShareSceneItemDetail&amp;id=38390834972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.taobao.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fut_sk%3D1.t7exUfP%252BUtMQADw88j9OJaVf_21380790_1407271417.Copy.ShareSceneItemDetail%26id%3D38390834972&d=LDk7oFq4p5IGC5z%2Fe%2B73Qozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalT